		(comment 3 "CERN-OHL-P v2 / Apache 2.0")
		(comment 4 "EphemerKey Authors")
	)
	(lib_symbols
	)

	(text "ephemerkey\nTop-Level Sheet\n\nSTM32U083KCU6 (UFQFPN-32): ULP Cortex-M0+, RTC time base, USB FS\n  - USART1 (PA9/PA10) <-> MAX-M10S NMEA/UBX (see GNSS sheet)\n  - TIM2_CH1 (PA0) <- GNSS TIMEPULSE 1PPS (RTC discipline)\n  - I2C1 (PB6/PB7) <-> LIS3DH (see Sensors sheet)\n  - USB DM/DP (PA11/PA12): provisioning / console\n  - SWD (PA13/PA14): debug header\n  - Button (PA5), LEDs green/red (PA6/PA7)\n  - LOCK_TX (PB0) + CODE_VALID strobe (PB1) -> companion lock board\n  - LSE 32.768kHz crystal on PC14/PC15 (RTC)\n\nInter-sheet buses: 3V3, GND, GNSS UART/PPS/EXTINT/RESET, I2C1, V_BCKP\n\nSee DESIGN.md for the full pin budget and architecture."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
